bottler
-------
Simple irc bot made in pure C.
Currently it can only connect to IRC.
Configuration is done by editing config.h and rebuilding.
You can also pass options via commandline parameters.

usage
-----
usage: bottler [options]

-h    help
-v    version

-s <host>       server hostname
-p <port>       server port
-n <nick>       bot nickname
-u <name>       bot username
-c <channel>    channel to join
-o <owner>      owner hostmask
